[I] A GUI, CLI and library for playing chess

[T] Cute Chess is a set of cross-platform tools for working with chess engines.
[T] It consists of: cutechess - a graphical user interface, cutechess-cli - a
[T] command line interface for automating chess engine matches and libcutechess
[T] - a libraby providing an interface for working with chesss engines.

[U] https://cutechess.com

[A] The cutechess authors
